# Ferthe Core API - Development Environment Variables

# ============================================
# Config Loading
# ============================================
# In development, all secrets are loaded from _config.json in the project root.
# Copy _config.json.example to _config.json and fill in your values.
#
# To test Key Vault loading locally, set:
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-service-principal-secret
# AZURE_KEYVAULT_NAME=kv-ferthe-core (optional, default)

# ============================================
# API Configuration (optional)
# ============================================
PORT=7000
HOST=0.0.0.0

# ============================================
# Store Configuration (optional)
# ============================================
# PRODUCTION=false (determines store type: json in dev, table in prod)
# CONTENT_DIR=../web/content